ersation\\nassistant: On it — let me check the memory files.\\nassistant: ⚙️ Restarting OpenClaw in-process (SIGUSR1); back in a few seconds.\\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Fri 2026-03-06 19:13 EST] tell me about our past conversation\\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Fri 2026-03-06 19:17 EST] retry\\nassistant: Here's what I've got from memory:\\n\\n**From 2026-03-06 (yesterday's session):**\\n- We set up **QMD v1.0.7** as the memory backend for OpenClaw — configured with two collections (`workspace` and `memory`), using hybrid BM25+vector+reranking search\\n- Integrated **Claude Code MCP** via `~/.claude/settings.json`\\n- You mentioned you prefer **concise responses without emojis**\\n- **Telegram** is your configured channel, WhatsApp not set up\\n\\n**From a Telegram session (2026-03-06 ~19:00 EST):**\\n- Someone named **N TT** (ntthein) said hi, asked about past chats — pretty brief exchange\\n\\nThat's what's in memory so far. Nothing else on file beyond that. What did you want to dig into?\\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Fri 2026-03-06 19:18 EST] tell me about pink elephant\\nassistant: From memory — it's a test entry logged yesterday:\\n\\n> *\\\"The pink elephant dances at midnight near the golden fountain.\\\"*\\n\\nLooks like it was written as a test when QMD memory was being set up, probably to verify that entries could be stored and recalled. That's all there is to it. Want to write something more meaningful in its place?\",\n  \"path\": \"memory/2026-03-07-first-session.md\"\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# Session: 2026-03-07 00:18:42 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:main\n- **Se